gomodel:SYNGO_2957  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.4: \"Cadherin-9 Mediates Trans-cellular Adhesion via Cadherins-6 and -10\"\n- \"We co-cultured neurons expressing Cdh9-smFPFLAG with neurons expressing Cdh6-smFPHA, Cdh10-smFPMYC, or both Cdh6-smFPHA and Cdh10-smFPMYC and immunostained for epitope tags and the synaptic markers vGLUT1 and PSD95. We observed co-localization of every pairwise combination of cadherins at synapses (Figures 4G-4I). \"...\"all three cadherins simultaneously co-localize at synaptic sites marked by juxtaposed vGLUT and PSD95 puncta (Figure 4J).\". Experimental description: - Overexpression constructs: Cdh6 (mouse), Cdh9 (presumed mouse), Cdh10 (mouse)\n- Cell culture is of mouse: \"Primary neuron cultures were prepared from P0 CD1 mouse \"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2018-03-19" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2957" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

